  "text": "The Bland-Altman Plot was used to estimate the bias and limits of agreement between measurements by the two methods [CITATION_1] . According to the recommendations by L. A. H. Critchley and J. A. H. Critchley, we quoted the mean CO (µ), the bias, the limits of agreement (95% CI), and the percentage error (±2 SD/µ) [CITATION_2] . BlandAltman plots and correlation curves were performed using GraphPad for Windows (Version 5.01, GraphPad Software, San Diego, California, USA).",
